{"tid":2091932,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"港金融從業員倫敦求職大增","createTime":"2020-07-03T03:06:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T03:14:09.000Z","uid":48083,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"35ab3c18527897dfca7a55f6c986a384e2741eba","tid":2091932,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"外電報道，中國政府上月宣布為香港設立《國家安全法》後，大批本港金融從業員向倫敦公司申請求職，港人購買倫敦物業的查詢量亦激增。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述招聘服務公司負責人透露，去年香港爆發社會運動後，英國已有大批投資銀行家拒絕接受到香港受聘。隨着《港區國安法》明確後，最近數周申請到英國就業的金融界人士數目大幅增加。<br />\n<br />\n有物業顧問公司發表報告指出，自去年3月以來，香港金融從業員對購買倫敦物業的興趣日濃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2511468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2511468&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBLTr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=48c01689\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2511468</a>"},{"pid":"e55bde957106bffd9ca3d41c886f8ab3d580bfa5","tid":2091932,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:07:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf6695cf7c14e41b86c28b649067cb5a65f12f4","tid":2091932,"uid":198536,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:09:32.000Z","msg":"倫敦金 <br />\n融從業員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9ab970334396754e288fa63cd63e448684b336","tid":2091932,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T03:09:42.000Z","msg":"倫敦樓價準備又火箭升多層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a746754c3c4ee40fda8fc23ca18671e8aa2ca0f1","tid":2091932,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cf6695cf7c14e41b86c28b649067cb5a65f12f4","tid":2091932,"uid":